# BUILDING PROCESS

## Build Commands
- **Development:** `./gradlew bootRun` or `./gradlew build && java -jar build/libs/*.jar`
- **Test:** `./gradlew test`
- **Build JAR:** `./gradlew clean build`
- **Run Tests:** `./gradlew test`

## Project Structure
```
src/
  main/
    java/
      vibe/selfdevleop/selfdevleop_backend_prepare/
        controller/     # REST API controllers
        service/        # Business logic
        repository/     # Data access layer
        entity/         # JPA entities
        dto/            # Data Transfer Objects
        config/         # Configuration classes
        exception/      # Custom exceptions
    resources/
      application.properties
      application-dev.properties
      application-prod.properties
  test/
    java/               # Test classes
```

# ENV VARIABLES FOR DEVELOPMENT

## application-dev.properties
```properties
spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/habit_launcher_dev
spring.datasource.username=dev_user
spring.datasource.password=dev_password
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
spring.jpa.show-sql=true
logging.level.org.springframework.web=DEBUG
```

# ENV VARIABLES FOR DEPLOYMENT

## application-prod.properties
```properties
spring.datasource.url=${DB_URL}
spring.datasource.username=${DB_USERNAME}
spring.datasource.password=${DB_PASSWORD}
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=validate
spring.jpa.show-sql=false
logging.level.root=INFO
server.port=${SERVER_PORT:8080}
```

## Environment Variables
- `DB_URL`: MySQL connection URL
- `DB_USERNAME`: Database username
- `DB_PASSWORD`: Database password
- `SERVER_PORT`: Server port (default: 8080)
